Guaranteed income bonds
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Net income or yield:
Non-taxpayers:                 6%-8%
25% taxpayers:                 6%-8%
40% taxpayers:             5.1%-6.8%
Key facts: Minimum age 18, minimum investment Pounds 2000, no maximum.
           Sold by insurance company representatives and independent
           financial advisers, guaranteed by the provider (life office)
Comment:   No capital growth. Could be a further tax charge on
           redemption for higher rate payers
